### ğŸ§  AI Fixes (Gemini)
Set your API key:

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here
```

or 
- change the `template.env` to `.env` and add `GEMINI_API_KEY`

Then run:

```bash
devseclint scan . --ai-fix
devseclint scan . --fix
```

